<li id="cite_note-Kirtland-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Kirtland_17-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Kirtland_17-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith1834" class="citation book cs1">Smith, Joseph (November 1, 1834). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://josephsmithpapers.org/paperSummary/revelation-book-2?p=1"><i>Kirtland Revelation Book</i></a>. Salt Lake City, Utah.: <a href="/wiki/LDS_Church" class="mw-redirect" title="LDS Church">LDS Church</a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/The_Joseph_Smith_Papers" title="The Joseph Smith Papers">The Joseph Smith Papers</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Kirtland+Revelation+Book&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City%2C+Utah.&amp;rft.pub=LDS+Church&amp;rft.date=1834-11-01&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjosephsmithpapers.org%2FpaperSummary%2Frevelation-book-2%3Fp%3D1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEndowment+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
