<li id="cite_note-68"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-68">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBrooks2015" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Joanna_Brooks" title="Joanna Brooks">Brooks, Joanna</a> (November 2, 2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=c2FjCgAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA286"><i>Mormon Feminism: Essential Writings</i></a>. Oxford, England: <a href="/wiki/Oxford_University_Press" title="Oxford University Press">Oxford University Press</a>. p.&#160;286. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0190248031" title="Special:BookSources/978-0190248031"><bdi>978-0190248031</bdi></a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>. <q>For men, 'the Lord' is Elohim who gives and later tests the man's names, signs, and tokens.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mormon+Feminism%3A+Essential+Writings&amp;rft.place=Oxford%2C+England&amp;rft.pages=286&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2015-11-02&amp;rft.isbn=978-0190248031&amp;rft.aulast=Brooks&amp;rft.aufirst=Joanna&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dc2FjCgAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA286&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AEndowment+%28Mormonism%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
